codex
I’ve got the fixes scoped: add `_start()` after `tevm` is set, correct the two documented `send` calls, widen the constructor overload for normal ethers `Interface`, and replace the ABI return/event type aliases with ethers-shaped ones. I’m applying those minimal edits now.
